      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just feels so heavy, you know? like i've spent my whole life preparing for a trip that doesn't actually have a purpose. i look at the waves and it's just... endless. there's no more novelty left. it feels like the only thing left to do is just stop moving and let the tide come in. does that make sense? like, when a journey is done, you're supposed to just finish it.",
